Package hu.bme.mit.theta.ltl.dsl.gen

Interface LTLGrammarListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
LTLGrammarBaseListener
public interface LTLGrammarListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by LTLGrammarParser.
